Lyrics:

لانعي حالي 
عاللي جرالي 
تعصف فيي رياح الويل 
مخاوي نجوم الليل

تاهوا دروبي 
شمسي غروبي 
يصطف الحزن بالدور 
يطلع هالنفس بالزور
 
علاش تروح تخليني
بدال الدم الي فيني
يجري سم وينهيني
 شوي شوي 

علاش تروح وبلايا 
تنسى طريقي وهوايا
كيف تتبدل النوايا 
الدم يصير مي 

ياما سندتهن يا أنا وهي أنا وحدي بقيت
أخدوك لحم .. وعضم؛ للذيابة رميوك
ياما ضويتلهن درب وبالعتم وحدي عميت
لولا نفيساً جوهرك ياجنيد ماباعوك.

ياما ياصاحب حذرت مالن أمان 
ياجود بجافوك بليالي وضحاهم ياما راهنت عليهن وخسرت الرهان لكن اصالة  معدنك بيسان تسواهم

علاش تروح تخلينيبدال الدم الي فيني يجري سم وينهيني
 شوي شوي علاش تروح وبلايا تنسى طريقي وهواياكيف تتبدل النوايا الدم يصير مي 


رغم اني ابن اليوم 
زعلان عاللي راح 
محرومة عيني النوم
كلي جراح

كونو العين بالعين
وحياة ضو العين
رد الصاع صاعين
حتى ارتاح

علاش تروح تخلينيبدال الدم الي فيني يجري سم وينهيني
 شوي شوي علاش تروح وبلايا تنسى طريقي وهواياكيف تتبدل النوايا الدم يصير مي

snippet.title: Wuyang | New Hero Gameplay Trailer | Overwatch 2
snippet.description:
Wuyang is finally here for some hydration domination!

As a prodigy from Wuxing University’s Water College, Wuyang redefines what it means to heal with a hybrid playstyle built on flow, precision, and constant disruption.

With his Xuanwu Staff and mobility-focused kit, you’ll be able to support or deal pressure depending on the situation, and reposition yourself with ease to escape danger or claim space. 

Make a splash as Wuyang during his limited-time trial Aug 14–18 and keep the party going when he officially arrives in Season 18.

Overwatch 2 is free to play for everyone on console & PC

_

snippet.title: Avatar: Fire and Ash | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
From Director James Cameron, watch the trailer for Avatar: Fire and Ash.
Experience the film only in theaters December 19.

With “Avatar: Fire and Ash,” James Cameron takes audiences back to Pandora in an immersive new adventure with Marine turned Na’vi leader Jake Sully (Sam Worthington), Na’vi warrior Neytiri (Zoe Saldaña), and the Sully family. The film, which has a screenplay by James Cameron & Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver, and a story by James Cameron & Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver & Josh Friedman & Shane Salerno, also stars Sigourney Weaver, Stephen Lang, Oona Chaplin, Cliff Curtis, Britain Dalton, Trinity Bliss, Jack Champion, Bailey Bass and Kate Winslet.

Denna episod handlar om Holly, en 19-åring som, på vägen hem från ett gaming-event, behövde stanna en natt på ett motel. Hennes vistelse på motellet blev dock LÅNGT från vad hon hade tänkt. Dessutom kunde spelet höra lite mer än vad jag trodde.. (host host *titeln på videon* host host)

snippet.title: Fortnite Battle Royale Chapter 6 Season 4: Shock 'N Awesome | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
You’re being tossed into the buggiest season yet with Fortnite’s Battle Royale Chapter 6, Season 4: Shock ’N Awesome!

The bugs out there? Vicious, relentless, swarming. The Island is an absolute mess of goopy nests and egg sacs. Prepare to stomp and smash the swarm with the O.X.R., the Island’s anti-bug military defense force.

If you’re serious about stomping roachies, then you’ll want to pick up new weapons issues by O.X.R. ike the Leadspitter 3000 minigun, Sweeper Shotgun, O.X.R. Rifle, Wrecker Revolver, or the laser-guided Swarmstrike rocket launcher.

And don’t forget about leveling up with the Shock ‘N Awesome Battle Pass to knock the socks off the swarm with style! New Outfits include:

UNSC Spartan
Yoo-mi
Agent Patch
Battle Gamer Mae
Lt. Ripp Slade
Onyx Winter
Green Ranger

Time to pelt pests, eliminating opposing enemies, and loot those Chests.

Good luck out there, soldier!

snippet.title: Skraja vi gå genom stan - Thomas Järvheden
snippet.description:
En uppdaterad Stockholmsskildring. 
Låttext finns längre ned:

Text: Peter Barlach 
Musik: Fred E. Ahlert
Videoproduktion: Erik Sandström på Widescreen media  AB https://widescreen.media

Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/artist/34SEvj5AzrGxeXqcOceERW 
Instagram: http://instagram.com/thomasjarvheden
Facebook: https://sv-se.facebook.com/ThomasJaervhedenOfficiellFansida

Text:
Åh, det är skönt när mitt Stockholm är grönt
Sakta gå hem genom stan
En kyss och sen går man sakta igen
Sakta en tur genom stan

Åh, det är natt och på avstånd hörs skratt
Och man går hem genom stan
En doft av weed från en ö här bredvid
smyger sig tyst genom stan

Utanför Grand står en Merca i brand
Nån kastar sten på en svan
I en krog-kö ropar nån du ska dö
Skraja vi gå genom stan

Nån drar sin kos efter en överdos
Nån möter en huligan
och tappar en tand och bryter en hand
Han håller på fel lag i stan

Från en balkong hörs en gäll klagosång
Därefter en duns som är dov
Sen blir det tyst, ingen säger ett knyst
Ingen som såg alla sov

Var det vinden som ven, nej det var en siren
Och ett öronbedövande dån
En fru går till sängs i sitt hus som sprängs
Skraja vi går därifrån

I fjärran hörs skott, en ungdom har fått
Vad någon bestämt han ska få
En gängkriminell får en smällkaramell
Skraja vi fortsätter gå

Benen som sand, din svett i min hand
Vi kryssar bland blåljus och rök
Och mest på tur, vi klarar oss ur
Ett överfallsrånförsök

På ett nattöppet fik är det skrik och panik
Det är upplopp vid Fridhemsplan
En gängskjutning här, en smash and grab där
Skraja vi gå genom stan

Åh det var skönt, när mitt Stockholm var grönt
Nu brinner det varstans i stan
En bön och sen, börjar allt om igen
Skraja gå hem genom stan
Skraja gå hem genom stan
Skraja gå hem genom stan

snippet.title: Lorna Shore - Prison Of Flesh (Official Video)
snippet.description:
Lorna Shore - Prison Of Flesh - Official Video. From the new album 'I Feel The Everblack Festering Within Me' - September 12 2025. Get it now: 
https://ifeeltheeverblackfesteringwithinme.com/
https://lornashoreband.com/
https://linktr.ee/IFTEFWM

ON TOUR W/
THE BLACK DAHLIA MURDER
SHADOW OF INTENT 
PEELINGFLESH
TICKETS: https://lornashoreband.com/pages/tour

"This song is exactly what I imagine a lot of people expected of us to put out. We took all the heaviest stuff we had, to create this incredibly dark, high-stress/tension song. I personally think the breakdown at the end of this is one of my favorites that we’ve ever written and I’m excited to see how people engage with this one.

The lyrics for this song are about my family and our history of dementia. The idea that the world is falling apart, and about the fear of losing touch with reality. “They’re coming to get me” is my way of personifying ‘demons’ or something that makes you feel like you’re losing pieces of yourself. The closer they get, the further detached you become until you’re nothing but a husk of fear and delusion." - WILL RAMOS

Lorna Shore - Prison Of Flesh - Official Video. From the new album 'I Feel The Everblack Festering Within Me' - September 12 2025. Get it now:

ON TOUR W/

SHADOW OF INTENT 
PEELINGFLESH
TICKETS: https://lornashoreband.com/pages/tour

"This song is exactly what I imagine a lot of people expected of us to put out. We took all the heaviest stuff we had, to create this incredibly dark, high-stress/tension song. I personally think the breakdown at the end of this is one of my favorites that we’ve ever written and I’m excited to see how people engage with this one.

The lyrics for this song are about my family and our history of dementia. The idea that the world is falling apart, and about the fear of losing touch with reality. “They’re coming to get me” is my way of personifying ‘demons’ or something that makes you feel like you’re losing pieces of yourself. The closer they get, the further detached you become until you’re nothing but a husk of fear and delusion." - WILL RAMOS

Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.description:
It's the Honest Trailer for K-Pop Demon Hunters! The movie that answers "what if Blackpink were all moonlighting as Buffy the Vampire Slayer?” It’s a story about friendship, saving the world, and never getting to 1st base with your crush because he's about 375 years older than you. Songs are super catchy though and the animation looks great. Do we like K-Pop now? I think we like K-Pop now!

snippet.title: HIM | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
What would you sacrifice to become the greatest of all time?

From Oscar® winner Jordan Peele and Monkeypaw Productions, producers of the landmark horror films Get Out, Us, Candyman and Nope, comes a chilling journey into the inner sanctum of fame, idolatry and the pursuit of excellence at any cost, featuring an electrifying dramatic performance from Marlon Wayans (Air, Respect).

Former college wide-receiver Tyriq Withers (Atlanta, the upcoming I Know What You Did Last Summer) plays Cameron Cade, a rising-star quarterback who has devoted his life, and identity, to football. On the eve of professional football’s annual scouting Combine, Cam is attacked by an unhinged fan and suffers a potentially career-ending brain trauma.

Just when all seems lost, Cam receives a lifeline when his hero, Isaiah White (Marlon Wayans), a legendary eight-time Championship quarterback and cultural megastar, offers to train Cam at Isaiah’s isolated compound that he shares with his celebrity influencer wife, Elsie White (Julia Fox; Uncut Gems, No Sudden Move). But as Cam’s training accelerates, Isaiah’s charisma begins to curdle into something darker, sending his protégé down a disorienting rabbit hole that may cost him more than he ever bargained for.

The film features a dynamic supporting cast including alternative comedy legend Tim Heidecker (First Time Female Director, Us) and Australian comic Jim Jefferies (The Jim Jefferies Show), plus MMA heavyweight fighter Maurice Greene and hip hop phenoms Guapdad 4000 and Grammy nominee Tierra Whack, all three in their feature film debuts.

Watson (Hala, Sprinter) for Monkeypaw Productions and is executive produced by David Kern and Monkeypaw’s Kate Oh.
